name: ExtensionOperationDefinition_Parameter
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.OperationDefinition.parameter` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `OperationDefinition.parameter` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `OperationDefinition.parameter` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`OperationDefinition.parameter` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `OperationDefinition.parameter` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4B: `OperationDefinition.parameter` 0..* `BackboneElement`
*  R4: `OperationDefinition.parameter` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `OperationDefinition.parameter` has is mapped to FHIR R4 element `OperationDefinition.parameter`, but has no comparisons.
Note available implied context: `OperationDefinition.parameter.part` because `OperationDefinition.parameter.part` is defined as a content reference to `OperationDefinition.parameter`.
